::Killfest/Greven/EndBringer::

Greven enters the pod, cramming himself into the back, Killfest 
sitting down in the co-pilots seat, moving it back as far as he can. 
The shuttle shakes slightly as EndBringer climbs on, adjusting his 
electric tentacles to magnetically attatch to the shuttles.

"Let's go," Killfest says, uncomfortable with his knees almost up to 
his chest. This shuttle was obvioustly not made for overgrown 
terrorists.
